{"tid":1938958,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"荷李活道公園四地點起火　台灣藝術家涉縱火被捕","createTime":"2020-03-23T01:27:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-23T05:31:35.000Z","uid":6497,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bddaa4d41ad0f520970bbe69f9168898ace68b2b","tid":1938958,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T01:27:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200323/4DCYVM7TJILBTZHCZE2PKKBREM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200323%2F4DCYVM7TJILBTZHCZE2PKKBREM%2F&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdKjPH3pfKCXBWMLigY0rPLs%3D&h=698a8dfd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200323%2F4DCYVM7TJILBTZHCZE2PKKBREM%2F&h=17303112\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200323/4DCYVM7TJILBTZHCZE2PKKBREM/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200323/large/1584915607_5d70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200323%2Flarge%2F1584915607_5d70.jpg&h=0bfc68b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200323/large/1584915607_6013.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200323%2Flarge%2F1584915607_6013.jpg&h=df7456e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200323/large/1584915614_d026.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200323%2Flarge%2F1584915614_d026.jpg&h=ae0e8d15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200323/large/1584915614_bf1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200323%2Flarge%2F1584915614_bf1f.jpg&h=9e1a7e5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上環荷李活道公園，凌晨3時許，公園外圍4處地方發生火警，一批雜物及枱凳起火焚燒，街坊發現報警，消防員趕至現場，開喉射水將火救熄，無人受傷，由於同時有多處地方起火，並在現場撿獲助燃劑，火警原因有可疑。<br />\n<br />\n燒毀一批枱凳分散在公園外圍四周，由街坊放置，供平日閒坐聊天或休息之用，消防員在現場調查期間，街坊發現荷李活道254號一間藝術畫廊起火，消防員趕至現場，發現店主在店內天井焚燒雜物，立刻將火救熄。<br />\n<br />\n姓林（40歲）店主手腳均有紋身，據悉他是台灣藝術家，移居來港後已取得香港身份證，曾接受報刊訪問。警員調查期間，林表現興奮，稱因感混濁燒雜物來淨化空氣，其間向記者舉起「V」字手勢，由於店舖與公園的最近火警現場僅相距約10米，警員懷疑林與縱火案件有關，將他拘捕帶返警署調查。"},{"pid":"5c8443a637b3b12433e041b7cf30141ff54fc9e7","tid":1938958,"uid":301666,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T01:28:59.000Z","msg":"有狗屋你反而唔燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1c629f833d6329ca6a40fe87f8b9b09760a653f","tid":1938958,"uid":68689,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T01:33:41.000Z","msg":"遮左對眼成個689咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddc4a0520788c1beaa367c260624b82f99d01bae","tid":1938958,"uid":223249,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T05:14:38.000Z","msg":"最慘啲路宿者，無啦啦啲家檔俾人燒"},{"pid":"014bd9cca00bda9f836dd81ec1448886509d7255","tid":1938958,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T05:16:36.000Z","msg":"白卡？"},{"pid":"26c9328796f9ae7d918fcd872d7fa6338f9dc39a","tid":1938958,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T05:18:05.000Z","msg":"high咗嘢？"},{"pid":"29d60fcc66f7882deba2e0fbcf0786663de6e82b","tid":1938958,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26c9328796f9ae7d918fcd872d7fa6338f9dc39a","tid":1938958,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T05:18:05.000Z","msg":"high咗嘢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T05:31:35.000Z","msg":"九成"}]}